      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PACKHAM ROSE (6) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at four of nine starts including two wins but missed the frame latest when fifth (22.38) over 380m at Townsville. Tends to go well on this box draw. Well placed here and can go close with a clear run. WAIKARIE VENOM (4) last raced on December 17 when seventh (31.26) over 510m at this track in a OPEN. Has a good record at this journey. Will go close here with a clear run. APOLLO'S SUN (3) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing seventh (24.52) at this track in a Grade 5. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the low draw. Can hit the frame this time. RUPEE RANGER (8) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
